00:10:21.246 --> 00:10:22.676 A:middle
All of the window chrome in the

00:10:22.676 --> 00:10:24.756 A:middle
background generally just melts

00:10:24.756 --> 00:10:26.466 A:middle
away, and the content becomes

00:10:26.466 --> 00:10:27.646 A:middle
the primary focus of your

00:10:27.646 --> 00:10:28.136 A:middle
