00:10:32.226 --> 00:10:33.996 A:middle
treat your content regions

00:10:33.996 --> 00:10:35.656 A:middle
inside of your windows to

00:10:35.656 --> 00:10:37.406 A:middle
optimize the content focus.

00:10:38.596 --> 00:10:39.926 A:middle
The first method was to just

00:10:40.066 --> 00:10:42.466 A:middle
generally go completely dark.

00:10:42.636 --> 00:10:43.946 A:middle
An app like Finder is a great

00:10:43.946 --> 00:10:45.076 A:middle
