00:10:45.136 --> 00:10:47.246 A:middle
possible because of the way that

00:10:47.246 --> 00:10:48.396 A:middle
the content is displayed.

00:10:48.936 --> 00:10:50.646 A:middle
Finder's content are displayed

00:10:50.646 --> 00:10:53.316 A:middle
as colorful file icons and so

00:10:53.316 --> 00:10:54.516 A:middle
the dark background really helps

00:10:54.606 --> 00:10:56.606 A:middle
the icons stand out as much as

00:10:58.106 --> 00:10:58.536 A:middle
possible.

